    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/45b22977f4f459d5d8361427fddfa383.poster.avif?t=1765957969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/45b22977f4f459d5d8361427fddfa383.webm?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/45b22977f4f459d5d8361427fddfa383.mp4?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>活到最后</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集幸存者，逃离被僵尸摧毁的世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFENSURVIVOR</strong>是一款策略游戏，您可以建造障碍物并部署幸存者来抵御僵尸。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用随机分配的单位，活到最后一刻！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>游戏玩法</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/8069574a7f758dd7169e44f2730b2c49.poster.avif?t=1765957969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/8069574a7f758dd7169e44f2730b2c49.webm?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/8069574a7f758dd7169e44f2730b2c49.mp4?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保护庇护所免受来袭的僵尸攻击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在庇护所周围建造墙壁，限制僵尸的路径。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部署单位以击败僵尸。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用击败僵尸获得的货币招募新的幸存者。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过保护庇护所15分钟获胜。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将招募的单位合成为更高等级的单位，利用更强的单位。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>幸存者专业化</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/bbbbaa861e7c22cdffb2440962fab676.poster.avif?t=1765957969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/bbbbaa861e7c22cdffb2440962fab676.webm?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/bbbbaa861e7c22cdffb2440962fab676.mp4?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作具有独特特性的多种兵种。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择幸存者，并通过合成功能获得更强大的幸存者。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找协同效应良好的幸存者组合。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败Boss以获得合成所需的货币。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ※<strong>有用提示</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以从建造菜单中建造和升级墙壁。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拖动底部的幸存者卡片将其放置在所需位置。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点击已部署的幸存者进行移动、晋升或合成。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点击运输机投放的补给箱，以获得对生存有帮助的神器或额外幸存者。</p></li></ul>",
